{"tid":1721520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"優勢絕對係我地個邊","createTime":"2019-11-14T16:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T11:25:31.000Z","uid":218313,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"018ab2cbb801b72e90b681c47a0848329698bbfc","tid":1721520,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:20:33.000Z","msg":"首先, <span style=\"color: red;\">休息撚散水撚</span>退散!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港共依家已經無晒棋, 所以尋晚先用下三流手法<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">煽動藍屍&quot;止暴制亂&quot; </span>=&gt; <span style=\"color: maroon;\">點知出左人命</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">黑社會行動</span> =&gt; <span style=\"color: maroon;\">班白痴玩到想綁架女仔</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我敢話優勢絕對係我地個邊:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">1&gt; 各大守城壯舉</span></strong><br />\n各大學手足, 基本上經過中大一役, 暫時係<ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>絕對安全</strong></span></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為攻打大學帶來既<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>國際輿論</strong></span>, 係現時港共同中共政府承受唔到<br />\n本來中共一直努力阻止人權法係美國通過, 尋日之後, 連最撚麻煩既Mitch McConnell 都開始轉口風, <ins>之前遊說努力可謂全部白費</ins><br />\n而日落國亦都少有地開口<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>所以政府係絕對唔可以再用硬性手法攻城</strong></span><br />\n只可以用軟性手法老嚇大家, 今日見到幾多風就知 (PLA, 撤師生等等)<br />\n(但係Dioxin 係真係有, 去到UC 都有雀仔死...手足小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>2&gt; 黎明行動絕對係渣中左春袋</strong></span><br />\n因為各大手足努力, 好多交通要道都被截<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">停課做到了</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">停巿黑警做到了</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果連<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>政經中心</strong></span>既要道都被截埋, 基本上全香港就已經停止運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真正被動三罷<br />\n所以點解油塘咁多狗, 就係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>3&gt; 示威目的達成</strong></span><br />\n好多手足去到呢一刻, 好似忘記左我地出黎示威目的係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>- 同政府講我地無放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 擾亂秩序, 增加政府管治成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n由港共依靠黑警開始, 基本上每一個動作都係幫緊我地<br />\n而且仲開始想玩人民鬥人民,  香港越亂, 就其實係幫緊我地完成我地<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒</span></strong>既目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要記住, 呢場仗係好長</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家發球權係我地度, 千祈唔可以縱容自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n習慣左無規管既暴力, 就只係純粹既發洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好令自己成為最討厭既藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住我地以武制暴既原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天佑我城<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫推</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f17b6ecbe598840554deab63a424485eef4a3a5d","tid":1721520,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T16:23:09.000Z","msg":"哇屌, 岩岩打完, 見到人權法玩 HOTLINE<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n6 個鐘就過!"},{"pid":"915df